title: Aussie bachelorette finds love in New Zealand (New Zealand Tourism Board)
text: ( Source : New Zealand Tourism Board ) Today it was announced that New Zealand is the destination for the season finale of the Australian reality series The Bachelorette - which will showcase New Zealand as the ultimate romantic destination
